<div class="container">
  <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Log In</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-6 px-lg-5">
      <p>Welcome back, fellow cosmic traveler! It's a delight to see you return to Astral Escapes, where the wonders of the universe await your exploration once more.</p>

      <p>At Astral Escapes, we cherish the opportunity to accompany you on your interstellar journey time and time again. Whether you're returning to revisit a favorite destination or embarking on a new adventure among the stars, your presence enriches our celestial community.</p>

      <p>As you step back into the fold, know that our team is here to welcome you with open arms and guide you on your cosmic quest. With each visit, you contribute to the tapestry of experiences that make Astral Escapes a beacon for adventurers across the galaxy.</p>

      <p>So here's to another voyage into the unknown, another chapter in your cosmic odyssey!</p>
    </div>
  <div class="col-6 px-lg-5">
    <%= simple_form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
      <div class="form-inputs">
        <%= f.input :email,
                    required: false,
                    autofocus: true,
                    input_html: { autocomplete: "email" } %>
        <%= f.input :password,
                    required: false,
                    input_html: { autocomplete: "current-password" } %>
        <%= f.input :remember_me, as: :boolean if devise_mapping.rememberable? %>
      </div>

      <div class="form-actions">
        <%= f.button :submit, "Log in", class: "btn btn-flat" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
